WEBVTT

00:00.287 --> 00:01.821
One, two , three, go.

00:01.889 --> 00:03.990
♪ My baby don't mess around ♪

00:04.058 --> 00:09.545
♪ because she loves me so,
and this I know for sure ♪

00:09.630 --> 00:12.365
♪ but does she really wanna ♪

00:12.433 --> 00:16.569
♪ but can't stand to see me
walk out the door? ♪

00:16.637 --> 00:19.005
<i>I'm not playing games here.</i>
<i>Don't threaten me.</i>

00:19.073 --> 00:20.640
I'm not afraid
of you people.

00:20.707 --> 00:24.010
I know what this is
really worth.

00:24.078 --> 00:25.578
How much longer
is this gonna take?

00:25.646 --> 00:26.946
I'm trying to conduct
business here.

00:27.014 --> 00:29.348
I just got to get a part
out of the van, Mr. Brooks.

00:29.416 --> 00:30.450
We'll be all set.

00:30.517 --> 00:33.286
♪ 'Cause we don't know how ♪

00:39.526 --> 00:40.893
<i>You take care of it?</i>

00:40.944 --> 00:42.528
Not yet.

00:42.596 --> 00:44.664
Listen, are you sure
about this target?

00:44.731 --> 00:47.667
<i>You're the only guy</i>
<i>in the business</i>

00:47.734 --> 00:49.669
<i>who asks these kinds</i>
<i>of questions.</i>

00:49.736 --> 00:51.537
<i>Brooks got himself</i>
<i>into this mess.</i>

00:51.605 --> 00:53.039
<i>That's all you need to know.</i>

00:53.107 --> 00:55.775
<i>Don't call me again</i>
<i>till it's done.</i>

00:57.000 --> 01:03.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:11.191 --> 01:13.092
<i>So don't threaten me.</i>

01:13.160 --> 01:14.494
♪ Shake it, shake it ♪

01:14.561 --> 01:18.631
♪ sh--sh--sh--shake it
like a polaroid picture ♪

01:24.571 --> 01:26.305
Yoga crap again, huh?

01:26.373 --> 01:27.657
I told you,
it's tai chi.

01:27.741 --> 01:29.108
There's a guy
on the phone,

01:29.176 --> 01:31.944
says he's an old friend
of yours--Donnelly.

01:40.387 --> 01:41.838
Yeah?

01:48.295 --> 01:50.596
So when was the last time
you been in there?

01:50.664 --> 01:53.166
<i>About seven years ago.</i>
<i>Things haven't changed much.</i>

01:53.233 --> 01:54.700
Same charming
clientele, huh?

01:54.768 --> 01:56.135
That's pretty safe
to say.

01:56.203 --> 01:57.970
Ain't nothing safe
about that place.

01:58.038 --> 01:59.872
Are you worried about me?

01:59.940 --> 02:01.807
I'm just saying,
that place, those people--

02:01.875 --> 02:03.910
that's part of your past.

02:03.977 --> 02:05.661
Don't you think it's better
you kept it there?

02:05.746 --> 02:08.080
It's just a conversation.

02:08.148 --> 02:09.882
So who's
this Donnelly guy?

02:09.949 --> 02:12.318
- Just a guy.
- Yeah, but a bad guy, right?

02:12.386 --> 02:13.986
See, 'cause that's
a bad-guy bar,

02:14.054 --> 02:15.821
so he must be a bad guy.

02:15.889 --> 02:18.124
Are you coming?
It's your last chance.

02:18.192 --> 02:20.826
Hell, no.

02:20.894 --> 02:24.297
I hate bad guys.

02:27.334 --> 02:30.703
♪ ♪

02:30.771 --> 02:34.540
♪ whatever you want ♪

02:34.608 --> 02:38.644
♪ whatever you need ♪

02:38.695 --> 02:43.316
♪ if you want me... ♪

02:43.383 --> 02:44.417
Ha ha.

02:44.484 --> 02:47.320
You don't write.
You don't call.

02:47.387 --> 02:51.524
Way to make an old buddy
feel forgotten.

02:51.592 --> 02:54.126
I haven't forgotten
anything.

02:56.563 --> 02:58.931
So what's so important that
I got to be here right away?

03:02.236 --> 03:03.803
This just came down.

03:03.870 --> 03:05.338
It's got a lot
of heat on it.

03:05.405 --> 03:07.206
You know I don't do
that kind of work anymore.

03:07.274 --> 03:09.642
It's not that side
of the job, Chance.

03:09.710 --> 03:11.477
They already hired somebody
to do the hit,

03:11.545 --> 03:13.579
and he's the best
in the business--

03:13.647 --> 03:15.848
you, seven years ago.

03:15.916 --> 03:22.355
♪ ♪

03:29.496 --> 03:30.696
Why are you
giving me this?

03:30.764 --> 03:33.099
I knew you'd be
interested, that's all.

03:33.166 --> 03:34.600
Might want to fix it.

03:34.668 --> 03:38.671
If you can't save her,
nobody can.

03:38.739 --> 03:41.407
Tell me everything you know
about this job.

03:41.475 --> 03:43.776
You know I can't give you
anything else.

03:43.844 --> 03:45.945
I'd be a dead man,
if I'm not already.

03:46.013 --> 03:47.947
The only thing
I can say is

03:48.015 --> 03:52.084
it goes down soon--
real soon.

03:58.058 --> 04:01.727
You torch the place,
I hope?

04:01.795 --> 04:03.595
We're taking the case,
starting right now.

04:03.647 --> 04:07.400
- Okay, what are the details?
- I don't know.

04:07.467 --> 04:10.269
- Then why is she being targeted?
- <i>I don't know.</i>

04:10.337 --> 04:13.839
Okay, so you want to tell me
why we're taking this case?

04:15.876 --> 04:18.911
Seven years ago...

04:18.978 --> 04:20.946
I killed her husband.

04:30.023 --> 04:35.564
